<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Good Friday</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 25, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
The empire justifies its existence <br></br>
with promises of safety and security, <br></br>
promises that hold no power <br></br>
unless the people live in fear.
</p>

 <p>
And so, a terrorist was released <br></br>
so that the Prince of Peace <br></br>
may be taken to be silenced.
</p>

 <p>
Lord, have mercy.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


